AKAKATHATHI sinqumo ngekusasa lakhe uNkk Patricia De Lille ngoLwesithathu omemezele ukuthi uzosigcina isinqumo sakhe sokusula njengeMeya yaseKapa. UDe Lille umemezele lezi zindaba engaphandle kweNkantolo eNkulu yaseWesterm Cape lapho afake khona isicelo sokuthi kuchithwe imibiko emibili eyenziwa abameli beBowman Gilfillan ebiphenya ngendlela abephethe ngayo umasipala. Noma udaba lusaqhubeka enkantolo, uDe Lille uthe akaguquki kwisinqumo sakhe sokusula kwesobuMeya wabe esememezela nokuthi uyalishiya iqembu leDA ngemuva kwesikhathi eside ‘ecindezelekile’ kuyona. Usayine incwadi yakhe yokusula njengeMeya emastebhisini khona enkantolo. UDe Lille usula nje usanda kubekwa icala lokukhwabanisa ngemuva kombiko weBowman oveze ukuthi bekwenziwa umkhonyovu ngamabhasi eMyCiTi. Omunye wabaphenywayo ngalezi zinsolo ukhomishina wezokuthutha osamisiwe emsebenzini, uMelissa Whitehead, okusolwa ukuthi uyathinteka ekukhwabanisweni kwethenda likaR286 million lamabhasi ahamba ngogesi. Ngesikhathi kuhlangane umkhandlu ngeledlule kwavunyelwana ngokuthi udaba ludluliselwe emaphoyiseni ukuze kuphenywe bonke abathintekayo. Ngesikhathi uhleli lowo mhlangano kwabamuncu kusula amanye amalungu awu-5 eDA esola le nhlangano ngokucwasa nokucindezela uDe Lille ngalezi zinsolo abathi abukho ubufakazi bazo. UDe Lille uthe uyasola ukuthi abammeli beBowman Gilfillan bebesebenzisana nosopolitiki ukumbhixa ngezinsolo zokuthi ubedla imali yabakhokhi bentela. 